    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've been reading online about how garlic supplements actually have a huge effect on preventing clots naturally. if i just really ramp up the dosage of garlic and eat lots of spinach and kale, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as the warfarin pills without all the side effects? it feels like a lot of unnecessary chemicals if i can just use what's in nature.",
